Identification : Given K and Smallest/Largest i.e Kth smallest or Kth Largest

if Given K and Smallest -> Choose Max heap -> Because largest element is root of binary tree and we keep popping after size of heap >K

if Given K and Largest -> Choose Min heap . -> Because smallest element is root of binary tree and we keep popping after size of heap >K

Element at K in heap is kth element smallest or largest for max and min heap respectively.

Use priority queue as min or max heap .